de.weltraumschaf.ebnf.ast.builder
Class GenericBuilder<P>

java.lang.Object
  de.weltraumschaf.ebnf.ast.builder.GenericBuilder<P>
Type Parameters:
P - Parent builder. Either RuleBuilder or GenericBuilder.
public class GenericBuilder<P>
extends Object

Generic builder provides interface to construct sub nodes for rule nodes. This class is parameterized with the type of the parent builder.

Author:
Sven Strittmatter
